    "Through Tavistock, Lewis owns Premier League soccer team Tottenham Hotspurs and has a stake in U.K. pub operator Mitchells & Butlers.",
    "He pleaded guilty to insider trading charges in 2024 for sharing information with his pilots and ex-girlfriend but was later pardoned by Trump in 2025, paying a $5 million fine.",
    "Born above a pub in London's East End, Lewis helped his family build a catering business. He sold it and became a currency trader.",
    "He is now living on his yacht, Aviva, in the Bahamas."
